        "headline": "USN-8082-1: GIMP vulnerabilities",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "Michael Randrianantenaina discovered that GIMP incorrectly handled certain malformed ICO files. An attacker could possibly use this to cause a denial of service or execute arbitrary code. (CVE-2025-5473) Seungho Kim discovered that GIMP incorrectly handled certain memory operations when running the despeckle plugin. An attacker could possibly use this to cause a denial of service or execute arbitrary code. (CVE-2025-6035)",
          "lang": "en"
